UR  - https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/030440769090123B
AB  - In this paper a new robust estimation method of linear regression models is proposed. The method is based on grouping and adjustment. The estimator is calculated by the OLS and WLS methods using adjusted dependent variables. Consistency and asymptotic normality of the estimator are proven.
